        "title": "Way More Than Just a Trampoline",
        "image_accordion_copy": "<p>JumpSport fitness trampolines are more than rebounders — they’re compact, low-impact fitness systems designed for cardio, strength, balance, and recovery. Built for home workouts and trusted by professional studios, they deliver powerful performance with less joint stress than traditional high-impact training.<\/p>",
