        "title": "Your Workouts, Built In — 60 Days Included",
        "copy": "<p>Every JumpSport Fitness Trampoline includes a <strong>60-Day Free Trial to JumpSport Fitness TV<\/strong>, our on-demand workout platform designed specifically for rebounder training.<\/p><p>You don’t have to guess what to do — just press play.<\/p><p><strong>What You Get:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>400+ on-demand workouts<\/li><li>Professional instructors<\/li><li>Beginner to advanced levels<\/li><li>Cardio, strength, balance, and recovery sessions<\/li><li>Programs built specifically for JumpSport trampoline dimensions and bounce<\/li><\/ul><p>Whether you're just getting started or training multiple times per week, Fitness TV helps you stay consistent and see results.<\/p>",
        "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/app-imgalt_1.webp"
      }
    },
